cu.explanation_en: Setting the SCTP control port to 99999 exceeds the valid TCP/UDP port range (1-65535), causing socket binding failure and preventing F1 connection establishment between CU and DU.

du.explanation_en: Modifying the front-haul timing advance Ta4 to [200, 250] introduces inconsistent timing parameters that do not align with standard 5G timing requirements, leading to synchronization failures between DU and RU.
